= SDL_HINT_VIDEO_X11_XRANDR =
A hint that specifies whether the X11 XRandR extension should be used.




== Values ==
{|
|0
|disable XRandR
|-
|1
|enable XRandR
|}


== Default ==
By default SDL will not use XRandR because of window manager issues.


